cat <<EOF
minecraft-server-center has been installed as a systemd service.

To start/stop minecraft-server-center:

sudo systemctl start minecraft-server-center
sudo systemctl stop minecraft-server-center

To enable/disable minecraft-server-center starting automatically on boot:

sudo systemctl enable minecraft-server-center
sudo systemctl disable minecraft-server-center

To reload minecraft-server-center:

sudo systemctl restart minecraft-server-center

To view minecraft-server-center logs:

journalctl -f -u minecraft-server-center

EOF